org.seedstack.io.spi

Interface TemplateLoader<T extends Template>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - template
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    StaticTemplateLoader<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractBaseStaticTemplateLoader

    public interface TemplateLoader<T extends Template>
    A TemplateLoader is associated to an AbstractTemplateRenderer. The association is made by the name of the renderer specified with templateRenderer.
